Ranger Help for: bringword
===========================

SYNTAX:      bringword on <player>
USAGE:       Wilderness
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     60
SKILL TYPE:  husbandry

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to send a small animal scout to find another
player and report back with their location. The animal will seek out the
target player and return with information about where they are. The
Ranger must be in wilderness terrain to call upon a scout animal. The
time it takes for the scout to return depends on how far away the target
player is. This skill is useful for locating friends or tracking targets.
